{"tid":534733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屌...遲下去飲，但係Ex都去...","createTime":"2018-01-20T06:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T16:08:27.000Z","uid":90,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d1f3060c6207e0cf8edd3b2e4b4696eca83623","tid":534733,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"Ex係大學同學<br />\n同佢拍咗有6年拖,其實一早都已經認定咗佢就係啱個個<br />\n當面對7年之癢,人人叫我真係要小心<br />\n就真係撞正有第三者介入(個個仲要係我師妹嚟!),結果同佢都係捱唔過7年,最後係不和平情況下分手&hellip;<br />\n你問我嘅,都算重傷&hellip;話晒都咁多年感情<br />\n所以自從分手之後,大家都真係冇聯絡<br />\n<br />\n咁有得避嘅場合都會避啦<br />\n但嚟緊有個老死舊同學結婚,叫我一定要去佢餐飲,<br />\n一諗起我個所謂前男友同個師妹都會出席,就覺得好頭痛好想甩底...<br />\n一嚟我仲未原諒到佢,二嚟我都唔想比佢見到我個殘樣<br />\n(呢幾年我不斷用工作黎麻醉自己,捱到個樣又老又殘...)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該點做"},{"pid":"611e79f44db995e8b72cddd7893c9dd337bcd717","tid":534733,"uid":2731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"唔好去"},{"pid":"b751a708629e0ed4d8ab020f09185b1aa047d570","tid":534733,"uid":78349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"病左"},{"pid":"56421300f41386667f9bd9a2f4e9c0f80e649223","tid":534733,"uid":19932,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 禮貌小小 大方小小。<br />\n比人感覺已經唔同左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫你去仲更加係要面對最真實嘅自己 唔洗逃避 <br />\n係成長嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6660532c05f2fcfc6115993e30b5feee35985a","tid":534733,"uid":27939,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"Beauty Exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fa257482bd2f838b4a3f604119b5418e5ae1f3","tid":534733,"uid":103966,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T06:42:38.000Z","msg":"揾個男仔扮男朋友，條仔要